message.content: Joule is an AI copilot that revolutionizes how users interact with their SAP business systems. It enables the companion of the Intelligent Enterprise, guiding users through content discovery within the SAP Ecosystem and providing transparent role-based access to relevant processes from anywhere. Joule aims to provide a unified and delightful user experience across SAP's solution portfolio.
